This high-quality Scotch® 311+ packaging tape provides superior holding power and reliable sealing for a wide range of applications. Made from kraft paper, these mailers feature a built-in layer of bubble wrap cushioning to ensure safe arrival.  The self-sealing design makes packaging quick and easy, while the discreet branding maintains a professional look.  Perfect for e-commerce businesses, online sellers, and anyone needing reliable and sustainable shipping solutions.

Title: TUFflex® 63 Ga. Cast Yellow Premium Stretch Film (20 in. x 5000 ft., 50 RL/SK)
Description:
**Bright Yellow Stretch Film Roll**

This vibrant yellow stretch film roll is perfect for a variety of applications where high visibility is required.  Ideal for securing and protecting goods during transport or storage, its bright color makes it easily identifiable.  The strong, durable film provides excellent protection against dust, moisture, and damage, ensuring your products arrive safely at their destination. This roll is a cost-effective solution for keeping your shipments safe and secure.

Title: PURELL® Professional Surface Disinfecting Wipes (110 Count Canister, 6/Case)
Description: Maintain a clean and hygienic environment with Purell Professional Surface Disinfecting Wipes. This canister contains 110 wipes, each effectively killing 99.9% of bacteria and viruses, including COVID-19, MRSA, *E. coli*, Strep, and Salmonella.  These wipes are effective against cold and flu viruses and require no rinsing.  Formulated without harsh chemicals, they offer a fresh citrus scent.  Perfect for homes, offices, and other settings requiring thorough disinfection.  Wipe dimensions: 7 in. x 8 in.

This stylish dispenser features a modern, elegant off-white marble design accented with subtle gold detailing, adding a touch of sophistication to any space.  Its compact design is perfect for high-traffic areas, and the easy-to-use functionality ensures efficient hand hygiene.  Experience the perfect blend of form and function with this premium dispenser, designed for both style and performance.
